title: Narrator Connect powered by NaviPlan
description: An API for accessing NaviPlan plan data for a client.

actions.title: Advisors_Get
actions.description: This operation retrieves a list of all of the Advisors in the plan.

actions.title: Advisors_GetById
actions.description: This operation retrieves an Advisor from the plan.

actions.title: Assumptions_GetByPlanidScenariotype
actions.description: This operation retrieves an object containing all assumptions for the specified plan.

planId.description: Id of the plan to retrieve data from (e.g. 1001-11-3). Default value is the first plan the user is authorized to access.

scenarioType.description: Type of plan to retrieve data from (0:Current-default, 1:Recommended)
